  <td>Rápido (sin lag de ajuste vs GPT-4 con fine-tuning)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td><strong>Inferencia (por 1M tokens)</strong></td>
  <td>Together AI (Llama 3.3 70B)</td>
  <td class="number">$0.18</td>
